v0.5.0 2026-02-20

* output an explicit null value when packages aren't found in the registry
* cache registry responses on disk for an hour to speed up subsequent runs
* add an optional --cache flag to control the cache location

v0.4.0 (2026-02-16)

* add an `id` field to the output, populated with a UUIDv7
* Fix calculation of direct:true when multiple versions of a package are in the dependency tree
* Add an optional `--compact` CLI flag that changes the output to a single line

v0.3.0 (2026-02-16)

* Always output the commit timestamp as UTC, regardless of the timezone in the raw commit
* Adjust some field names in the output to make it obvious they're timestamps, not dates

v0.2.0 (2026-02-15)

* remove the optional --manifest-path flag, replace it with an optional positional argument that points to a target directory

v0.1.0 (2026-02-09)

* Initial release
